From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude.ai.2026@simonlaux.de>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 16:57:21 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 57/58] web-app: mark fork-added settings with a small sloth
 badge

Settings that exist only in SlothfulChat (community-suggestion toggles,
the three experimental fork features, the analytics opt-out) get a small
sloth emoji after their label with an explanatory tooltip, so users can
tell fork additions from upstream Delta Chat settings. Threaded as a
'forkAdded' flag through SettingsSwitch/DesktopSettingsSwitch.
